      <h2 id="overview">Project Overview</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--muted)">Designed and executed file transfer operations and networking troubleshooting to fix connectivity and service-binding issues.</p>

      <h2>Tasks & Achievements</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Implemented reliable SCP transfers and diagnosed common errors (paths, permissions, auth).</li>
        <li>Inspected active ports and service bindings using <code>ss -tulnp</code> and <code>lsof</code>.</li>
        <li>Diagnosed firewall-related failures and validated rules with UFW and iptables checks.</li>
        <li>Used <code>curl</code>, <code>ping</code>, and <code>traceroute</code> for endpoint testing and latency diagnosis.</li>
      </ul>

